{{PREAMBLE}}

# /status — CEO Dashboard

Quick executive view of all PM-managed work. No details you don't need,
all the signals you do.

---

## Step 1: Discover sprint logs

```bash
{{SLUG_SETUP}}
```

Find all PM sprint logs for this project:

```bash
ls -t ~/.gstack/projects/$SLUG/pm-sprint-*.json 2>/dev/null
```

If no sprint logs found, check if there are any review logs:

```bash
ls -t ~/.gstack/projects/$SLUG/*-reviews.jsonl 2>/dev/null
```

If nothing exists:
```
No PM sprints found for this project.
Run /pm <issue-url> to start one.
```

---

## Step 2: Parse sprint data

For each sprint log file, read it and extract:
- `sprint_id`, `issue.number`, `issue.title`, `issue.type`
- `current_stage`, `started_at`, `completed_at`
- `metrics.bugs_found`, `metrics.decisions`, `metrics.lines_changed`
- `blockers` (any active blockers)
- Stage statuses and durations

Classify each sprint as:
- **ACTIVE** — `completed_at` is null
- **COMPLETED** — `completed_at` is set
- **BLOCKED** — has active blockers

---

## Step 3: Present the dashboard

Output the dashboard in this format:

```
=== CEO DASHBOARD — <project name> ===
Updated: <now>

ACTIVE SPRINTS
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  #   Issue                    Stage      Elapsed   Bugs  Blockers
  ─── ──────────────────────── ────────── ──────── ───── ────────
  123 Add user notifications   review     12m       2     0
  456 Fix login timeout        build      8m        0     0
  789 Refactor auth middleware  [BLOCKED]  25m       1     1
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

BLOCKED (needs CEO attention)
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  #789 — Refactor auth middleware
  Blocker: Critical review finding — SQL injection in query builder
  Waiting for: CEO decision (escalated 3m ago)
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

RECENTLY COMPLETED (last 7 days)
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  #   Issue                    Duration  Bugs  Lines   PR
  ─── ──────────────────────── ──────── ───── ─────── ────
  100 Add dark mode toggle     18m       1     142     #201
  101 Fix CSV export encoding  9m        0     37      #202
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

TEAM PERFORMANCE (this project)
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Sprints completed:  12
  Avg duration:       14m
  Avg bugs/sprint:    1.3
  Bug escape rate:    8% (found in QA, not review)
  Auto-decided:       89% of decisions
  Escalation rate:    11%
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
```

**Formatting rules:**
- Active sprints sorted by elapsed time (longest first — these might need attention)
- Blocked sprints always shown prominently with the blocker reason
- Completed sprints limited to last 7 days, sorted by completion time (most recent first)
- Performance metrics calculated across ALL sprints for this project
- If there are no active sprints, skip that section
- If there are no blockers, skip that section
- If there are no completed sprints, show "No completed sprints yet"

